Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈阿密登陆站 沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:02:58.04,ruby,NTP,0000,0110,0000,,Miami Landing Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信卫星呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到了轨道上扬陆城的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合总部、支部的通信全部中断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行部队被全灭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到了一架敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver-22？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干扰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先行的Silver小队好像已经和敌人接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机展开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击一切敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的原始人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪在神的威光之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.14,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1418,0)}北京／10:34
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是顺服呢 还是毁灭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只能二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.45,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1418,0)}马普托／04:47
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:48.26,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe out vermin Barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:53.93,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,With the supreme key that we hold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:59.48,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Her death delivered the truth to us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:03.69,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our love, and Sorrow, Anger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:10.12,INEN,,0000,0000,0000,,The declaration of war
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.05,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1418,0)}东京／13:26
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星重甲骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蝼蚁没有任何区别…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁迪欧伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该马上向新芦原进军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们在公主的命丧之地挂起国旗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯就更加出师有名了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我就是这样打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首要任务是先镇压降落区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 库鲁迪欧伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必将这件事交给我托利尔兰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.07,ruby,NTP,0380,0000,0000,,Trillram
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是报答长久以来您对我的知遇之恩的绝佳机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给你吧 托利尔兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到当地的责任者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并搞清公主遇害的详尽真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}紧急报道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就在刚刚 世界各地的主要都市受到了火星巴斯帝国军的军事攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0.5\shad0\pos(916,706)}巴斯帝国军开始了军事攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:12.72,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,0)}新芦原市／渡轮码头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在 由于原因不明的通信障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各地的详细受害情况还不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}政府认为巴斯帝国的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}导致通信网严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有足够的空间供给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要着急 慢慢地冷静地行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新芦原的市民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避难公告已经发布了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有还没来得及离开的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我们也被叫来帮忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 因为人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没办法反抗韵子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是帮忙干学生会的活那倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果这场战争扩大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总有一天也会被征兵的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备役也要等高中毕业才征吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:07:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…如果战局拖下去造成兵力不足的话 我们或者就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子 10点方向发现了一家子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真假啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屮火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 因为下达了待机任务 所以姐姐没办法去接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说乘雪姐的车去避难吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你还在家里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没和大家一起跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…还可以这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要学会随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么万一的话 要相信自己做出决断
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我不是一直有和你说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Penivia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让巡逻中的运输车把我带上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点去避难的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新芦原的全域已经发布了避难警告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是旅行者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听懂我说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来能听得懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样做很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可以保持这个姿势让我问你几个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓避难公告是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为火星人的袭击 据说东京已经陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要去相关部门来传达我们平安无事的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大使馆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得在这种情况下 他们还在正常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的巴斯公主暗杀事件之后 地球联合…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟拉姆公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她并没有参加游行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不习惯地球的重力 身体不适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找人替代了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解您的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个富有个性的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输车马上就会到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚给韵子发了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯雷因·托罗亚特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.80,ruby,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不敢相信竟然会由你来当我的领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奉库鲁迪欧伯爵之命前来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不要拖我的后腿哦 地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这个时候车没油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好感谢我哦 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样哦 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别给我光明正大的偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯？不…北欧人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新芦原还真是少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是美女就非常欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立大功了呢 伊奈帆 给你10分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KG-7 Areion！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带应该已经完成避难了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音 是雪姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说阿奈也在上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 重甲骑兵队出动了就说明敌人会攻到这所城市里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东京那边有高热源体正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个区域也成了预想交战区域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果不通过这里的话是没办法到达渡轮码头的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先找个安全区域然后跑到那边去避难！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会在这里阻止他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1时方向 敌人的飞机编队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地来送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但首先 先警告他们一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标进入视野 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.78,ruby,NTP,0000,0200,0000,,Target merge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全弹命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌…敌人健在！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫发无损！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群渣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀 哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库鲁迪欧伯爵根本就没把你给教导周全嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我托利尔兰来好好教导你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是战争的乐趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部来电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行部队已经和敌人的飞行部队接触
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在交战！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？电波的状态不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正使用强力的妨碍电波扰乱这边的指挥系统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和15年前是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年前个屁啊 这个诈骗师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我被抓尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来掩护你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死到临头还挣扎的人可不美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从高处俯视过去的同胞们惨死的心情如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行部队全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的飞行部队仍在向新芦原接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加快脚步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:13:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我们的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 按照缔约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能得到骑士的称号 凯旋回到母星巴斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来辛苦你了 莱埃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.76,ruby,NTP,0340,0000,0000,,Rayet
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到达目的地上空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 把我放下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nilokeras 切断连接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.08,ruby,NTP,0190,0000,0000,,disconnect
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托利尔兰爵士  久候您多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦你们完成了重大使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 各位沟渠老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后如果让你们多嘴地到处吱吱叫 我可不高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是只可爱的小老鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会放你跑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了敌人的重甲骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 它正在袭击平民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击 一口气解决掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持激光通信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要破坏队形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 首先保护平民！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？子弹没有作用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢准尉 去保护幸存者 我来掩护你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠戸上尉 这可是我的队！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便命令他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经确保了平民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榴弹炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:36.65,ruby,NTP,0000,0070,0000,,Grenade
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了你别来号令!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的身体到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我狠狠地打！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的人都收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续猫抓老鼠的游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 界冢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠戸上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于自己的软弱 还是死于有勇无谋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是觉得自己做出了一个有尊严的选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠戸上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总司令部 请回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总司令部！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我们就一直在原地绕圈子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我怎么办啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是界冢雪准尉 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上那个孩子 马上离开这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢准尉 到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军曹！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别浪费我精力 老鼠！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韵子 再快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在加速了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被它追上的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太重了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹车！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处乱窜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起助！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要救雪姐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就可以甩掉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你们一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起助…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩过头了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩啊 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经不会追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 伊奈帆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箕国呢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢准尉 我是鞠戸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠戸教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界冢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 火星人正在追你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还没有去攻击渡轮码头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能地去牵制他 但不要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要活着回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈帆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是刚刚那家伙还在追着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 趁这个机会也许可以让乘坐难民的渡轮出港
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们去当诱饵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走地下管线走廊的话 就可以从这里通往学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 要做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了机库 那里有练习机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实弹训练的弹药也留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就轮到我们来代替雪姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那架火星重甲骑兵战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“地球上最长的一天”
